headline: Cinnamon Beach Vacations Now Offers Luxury and Premium Rental Properties on Homes & Villas by Marriott Bonvoy
summary: PALM COAST, Fla., August 14, 2025--Cinnamon Beach Vacations now offers luxury rentals on Homes & Villas by Marriott Bonvoy, connecting Flagler’s coast to global travelers.

headline: Marriott Executive Apartments Expands in Malaysia, Introducing an Enriching Urban Retreat in the Heart of Kuala Lumpur
